{
  "texts": [
    "A potential problem could be finding staff willing to bridge, commit themselves and try to cooperate closely to prevent and solve conflicts.",
    "Bridging staff are familiar with the involved cultures and thus can help avoid or resolve cultural conflicts.",
    "Bridging staff can foresee the challenges and plan the project so that there will not be difficulties.",
    "Strong competence of a chairman of these teams is needed.",
    "Face-to-face meetings are important for immediate handling of conflicts and disagreements."
  ]
}